    given-names: Michal
    affiliation: "Evangelical Theological Faculty, Comenius University in Bratislava"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4730-5739"
  - name: "TEPALIT Project"
    affiliation: "APVV-24-0484"
repository-code: "https://github.com/michalvalco/apvv2026-hymnals"
url: "https://michalvalco.github.io/apvv2026-hymnals/"
abstract: >
  Open digital companion to the monograph chapter "Dogmatická komparácia
  luteranizmu a českých konfesií (utrakvizmus, Jednota bratská) v zrkadle
  liturgických a hymnologických prameňov (16.–18. storočie)."
  Includes a four-layer theological taxonomy (loci, confessional positions,
  hymnic evidence, hymn-pair dossiers) released as versioned CSV data, a
  parallel-text viewer (Synoptikon), an intertextual network graph, and a
  bilingual (Slovak/English) case-study evidence layer for the Lutheranisation
  thesis. Distinguished by a three-axis epistemic transparency framework:
  epistemic status (claim type), evidentiary strength (textual evidence
  quality), and verification status (whether the project has personally
  collated primary witnesses).
keywords:
